room_title: Escape room "Bio Lab" by Escape The Room Oregon in Eugene
room_description: You are taking a tour of the bio lab. When all of the sudden the Lab is on lock-down. There has been a contamination leak. You must decipher the clues, puzzles and hidden messages in order to turn on the scrubbers and unlock the door before the contagion spreads outside the lab. You only have 60 minutes before the contamination take effect. Do you have what it takes to survive and escape the Bio Lab?
